nodes.text: Sector One was a location on the Core World of Anaxes used by the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Battle of Anaxes. During the battle, a Republic LAAT/i gunship carrying Clone Force 99, Clone Commander CC-2224, Clone Captain CT-7567, ARC trooper CT-5597, and CT-6116 traveled near Sector One, where it was spotted by Separatist scouts. A scout proceeded to contact an OOM command battle droid in Sector One to alert them, and DSD1 dwarf spider droids shot down the gunship.

Sector One first appeared in The Bad Batch, an episode of Star Wars: The Clone Wars that was first shown as a story reel at Celebration Anaheim on April 17, 2015. On April 29, 2015, the episode was uploaded to StarWars.com. The episode was later completed and released on Disney+ on February 21, 2020 as the premiere of The Clone Wars: Season Seven. The subtitles on Disney+ revealed the capitalization of Sector One.
